snippet.title: Rivals 2 Gameplay - BioBirb (Wrastor) vs Trace (Ranno) Riptide 2023 Demo
snippet.description: I got the chance to play a game of Rivals 2 this weekend at Riptide! Waited 3 hours to get this one game in and it was 100% worth it. I'm gonna try to get more Rivals 2 gameplay videos out at future events I go to, I still want to try out Fleet / Zetterburn / Kragg.
